room_title: Escape room "The Panic Room" by Inland Empire Escape Rooms in Riverside
room_description: You wake up on a hard, cold stone floor. You can't remember how you got here, but there are several others locked up in this asylum with you. Can you and your newfound friends escape the eerie Kimberly Asylum before the harsh orderlies come for you? The lobotomy is scheduled to start in an hour, and you must take your chance to escape before the opportunity vanishes completely.
